<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - PaboCafe</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
</head>
<body class="Bodys">
    <header ="Contents">
        <h1>PaboCafe</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to PaboCafe, where we serve our customers with delightful drinks and a wide variety of coffees. Our passion for coffee drives us to source the finest beans and craft each cup with care. Whether you are looking for a classic espresso, a rich cappuccino, or a refreshing iced coffee, we have something to satisfy every coffee lover's palate.</p>
            <p>At PaboCafe, we pride ourselves on being known as the best coffee maker in town. Our baristas are dedicated to creating the perfect cup every time, ensuring you leave with a smile on your face and a skip in your step.</p>
            <p>Join us at PaboCafe and experience the best coffee in town, served with a smile.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <section class="car-stats">
        <div class="stats">
            <div>
                <h1 class="counter"
                    data-target="5"
                    data-speed="50">
                    0
                </h1>
                <h1>Stars</h1>
                <h5>STARS RATING</h5>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="counter"
                    data-target="8"
                    data-speed="150">
                    0
                </h1>
                <h1>Branches</h1>
                <h5>NUMBER OF BRANCHES</h5>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="counter"
                    data-target="1532"
                    data-speed="50">
                    0
                </h1>
                <h1>Followers</h1>
                <h5>SOCIAL MEDIA FOLLOWERS</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        </section>
</body>
</html>
